  </div>

  <!-- About -->
  <div class="container about">
    <div class="row">
      <h2 class="section-header center custom-header" id="about">About</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <p class="flow-text light-text">
        The phrase "Money on the Board" originates from a hockey tradition where a coach would post money on the locker room board as an incentive for players to score goals and to win key games.
      </p>
      <p class="flow-text light-text">
        In the online hockey community, this tradition has evolved into a grassroot fundraiser where fans can make pledges based on in-game events and have all proceeds go to a charity of their choosing. An example of this online phenomenon is <a class="about-a" href="https://twitter.com/bonksmullet">Bonk's Mullet</a> <a class="about-a" href="http://www.bonksmullet.com/p/sensmotb.html">"Sens MOTB"</a>, the inspiration for this project.
      </p>
      <p class="flow-text light-text">
        We at MOTB created this application to streamline Bonk's Mullet's MOTB process and to make it available for hockey fans everywhere. Enjoy.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

